      "raw_text": "given the Lidgerwood-Kenwood\ndistrict when improvements under\nway are completed by the Wash\nington Water Power Co.\n\n\nTheh Lidgerwood line is being\ndouble tracked from Bridgeport:\navenue to West avenue, a distance\nof half a mile, and double track\nwill be laid on the Aston street line\nalmost to it's junction with the\nLidgerwood line. The Aston line is\nalso being extended on a single\ntrack to Rowan avenue, half\nmile farther north.\n\n\nWhen these improvements are\ncompleted the company will prob\nably run it's tripper service during\nthe rush hours of the morning anc\nevening to a junction of the two\nlines at Nevada street and Prince\nton avenue, and will sprobably give\nbetter service on the regular\nschedule in addition."
